Enrollment and contributions to an IRA under the
program, including withholding by covered employers of employee payroll, rights
of covered employees, and obligations of covered employers;

Withdrawals, rollovers, and direct transfers from
an IRA under the program in the interest of facilitating portability and
maximization of benefits;

Phasing in the enrollment of eligible covered
employees by the size or type of covered employer, beginning with the initial
applicability date specified in this chapter;
